parameters:
(No way... us getting easily restrained like
this...)

A magic spell has been cast in this room to detect
intruders.

Did you think you could explore just because
there's a magic research presentation?
For now, please let me put on some clothes.

It seems like you have no remorse. Why did you try
to infiltrate the magic research?

(It seems like they have no intention of listening
to us. It's frustrating, but given the
circumstances, there's nothing we can do.)

Because it piqued my curiosity. I mentioned before
that when something is hidden, it only makes me
want to explore even more.
I said there would be no next time.

Well... I intended to just take a peek without
getting caught, you know.
I see. In that case, you will be expelled.
Please wait! Is there any way to avoid expulsion?
I'll accept anything else, so please.

I finally got into the magic academy I've always
admired. I don't want to be expelled like this.

Yes, but... I can't accept being expelled just for
entering the club room.

Those who cannot follow the rules are not worthy
of Caledony Magic Academy.

We can't raise a magician who would break taboos
in the future.

In the first place, you didn't just enter, did
you?

...  Note: The ellipsis (...) indicates a pause or
hesitation in speech.

Is this semen? Geez, didn't you use any
contraception?

It's useless. It can't be solved with the power of
students.

(...I can't muster any strength. Is it impossible
even for Amelia?)

Your pussy is all wet and sticky, tell me yourself
what you did.
If I do that, can I have my expulsion revoked?

You don't have to... It's not like you'll get
expelled anyway.

No, I finally got in. If I get expelled, I won't
have another chance to learn magic.

(Damn... Making Amelia endure this for the sake of
the mission...)

That's a good attitude. Now, tell me what you were
doing. The men should stay quiet.
I was having sex with Masamune.

What kind of sexual desire makes you horny in a
place like this, where there are monsters?
I bet the man was being forceful.
No... I was the one who initiated it.
Hmph, so you wanted it that badly.

Yes... We had just started dating, so I couldn't
resist.
What is it? Do you want to be expelled?
You're not hiding anything dangerous, are you?
Was sex with your boyfriend pleasurable?

Hm, it doesn't seem like a particularly large
penis, but how does it compare to other men?
I haven't... done it with anyone else.
What? Despite having a playful appearance.
Then, let me teach you about real sex.

This is the last chance. If you do this, I'll
cancel your expulsion.

Cursed magic is my specialty. Stay quiet and
behave.

(Don't joke around! Is that what a teacher should
do?)
Are you really going to revoke my expulsion?

(It's not like failing this mission would be a big
deal...)

I'm sorry, Masamune-kun. But I can't let myself
get expelled.

Don't worry, I'm fine with this. But I wonder if
my illusions have already been shattered...
(There's no way I would be disappointed...)
